<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Luvics Pratinho - Combo Exclusivo</title>
    
    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700;800;900&family=Outfit:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <script defer src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>

    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Poppins', 'sans-serif'],
                        display: ['Outfit', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                    colors: {
                        brand: {
                            50: '#fffaf5',
                            100: '#f1dec7',
                            200: '#e7b74d',
                            500: '#f6a313',
                            600: '#ef9a00',
                            700: '#c96913',
                            800: '#b85f16',
                            900: '#5b4330',
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>

    <style>
        [x-cloak] { display: none !important; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { background-color: #fffaf5; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #5b4330; }
        
        .card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #f1dec7;
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
            position: relative;
        }

        .btn-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f6a313, #ef9a00);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #d68b0e;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn-gradient:active {
            transform: translateY(3px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 0 #d68b0e;
        }
        
        /* Animação do Fogo */
        @keyframes flicker {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 2px #fff); }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1.1); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px #ffeb3b); }
        }
        .animate-flicker { animation: flicker 0.8s infinite alternate ease-in-out; }
        
        /* Animação de Pulsação do Botão */
        @keyframes pulse-cta {
            0% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #d68b0e, 0 0 0 0 rgba(246, 163, 19, 0.4); }
            70% { transform: scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #d68b0e, 0 0 0 15px rgba(246, 163, 19, 0); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 5px 0 #d68b0e, 0 0 0 0 rgba(246, 163, 19, 0); }
        }
        .animate-pulse-cta { animation: pulse-cta 2s infinite ease-in-out; }

        @keyframes pulse-soft {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
        }
        .animate-pulse-soft { animation: pulse-soft 3s infinite ease-in-out; }

        /* Animação de Entrada suave */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }
        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body x-data="{ 
    showSticky: false,
    init() {
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    entry.target.classList.add('active');
                }
            });
        }, { threshold: 0.1 });
        
        document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
    }
}" @scroll.window="showSticky = (window.pageYOffset > 500)">

    <!-- Top Banner -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-brand-500 text-white font-black text-center py-3 px-4 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-lg border-b border-orange-400 rounded-b-2xl">
        <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-[10px] md:text-sm">
            <div class="animate-flicker">
                <i data-lucide="flame" class="w-6 h-6 fill-yellow-300 text-orange-200"></i>
            </div>
            <span>HOJE: 3 eBooks pelo preço de 1 • <s class="opacity-70">R$79,80</s> por R$14,90</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <main class="max-w-[620px] mx-auto px-4 pt-6">

        <!-- Hero -->
        <div class="card reveal active">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-display font-black leading-tight text-brand-700 mb-4 text-center md:text-left">
                Seu bebê recusa comida e você não sabe mais o que fazer?
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-brand-800/80 italic text-center md:text-left">
                Existe uma forma simples de resolver isso de uma vez por todas.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Dores com Animação -->
        <div class="card reveal">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i data-lucide="users" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500"></i>
                Você vive alguma dessas situações?
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-50/50 p-4 border-l-4 border-brand-500 rounded-r-xl font-bold shadow-sm reveal">
                    <span class="text-xl">😣</span> Medo constante de oferecer os alimentos errados
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-50/50 p-4 border-l-4 border-brand-500 rounded-r-xl font-bold shadow-sm reveal">
                    <span class="text-xl">😣</span> Seu bebê fecha o rostinho ou joga a comida no chão
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-50/50 p-4 border-l-4 border-brand-500 rounded-r-xl font-bold shadow-sm reveal">
                    <span class="text-xl">😣</span> Falta de criatividade e tempo para preparar algo novo
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-brand-50/50 p-4 border-l-4 border-brand-500 rounded-r-xl font-bold shadow-sm reveal">
                    <span class="text-xl">😣</span> A hora da refeição virou um momento de puro estresse
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- VSL -->
        <div class="card text-center overflow-hidden reveal">
            <div class="text-2xl font-display font-black text-brand-800 mb-6 font-bold">Assista antes de decidir (2 min)</div>
            <div class="relative aspect-video rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-black">
                <iframe class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <a href="#comprar" class="btn-gradient w-full block mt-6 text-white font-black py-4 px-8 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">
                QUERO O COMBO AGORA
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- PRODUTO PRINCIPAL - ATUALIZADO -->
        <div class="card text-center reveal">
            <div class="relative inline-block group">
                <img 
                    src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuanFaria/luvics/09e23495ff4ddb6e314b5376667f56f524917a9c/pratinho/imagens/ebook3d.png" 
                    class="w-56 mx-auto relative z-10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-3" 
                    alt="Receitinhas Saudáveis"
                    referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
                >
                <div class="absolute -bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-40 h-8 bg-black/10 blur-xl rounded-full translate-y-2"></div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-black text-brand-800 mt-6 tracking-tight">Receitinhas Saudáveis</h2>
            <p class="text-brand-900/60 font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-xs mt-1 italic">+ de 101 métodos e receitas práticas</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bônus -->
        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 to-white text-center reveal">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-800 mb-6 justify-center flex items-center gap-2">
                🎁 Bônus inclusos SOMENTE HOJE
            </h2>
            <div class="bg-brand-50 border-2 border-dashed border-brand-200 rounded-[28px] p-8 text-center relative">
                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuanFaria/luvics/52b4a8e6a62033d54065c9da2583981d2a384f2d/pratinho/imagens/bonus.png" class="max-w-xs w-full mx-auto drop-shadow-2xl" alt="Bônus" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
                
                <div class="text-left mt-6 space-y-3">
                    <p class="font-bold text-brand-900 flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0"></i> Bônus 1: Meu Filho Não Quer Comer? O que fazer?</p>
                    <p class="font-bold text-brand-900 flex gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0"></i> Bônus 2: Lista de Alimentos Saudáveis e seus beneficios (por idade)</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-brand-100">
                    <span class="text-brand-900/60 block mb-1">De <s class="text-red-500">R$29,90</s> cada por</span>
                    <span class="text-4xl text-green-600 font-black font-display underline decoration-4 underline-offset-8 block">GRÁTIS</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Depoimentos -->
        <div class="card reveal">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-black text-brand-800 mb-8 text-center">O que as mamães estão dizendo...</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-brand-50/30 p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-brand-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-center reveal">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/ana_mom/100/100" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md" alt="Ana" referrerPolicy="no-referrer" />
                    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                        <div class="font-bold text-brand-900 text-lg">Ana Silveira</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-orange-600 font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Mãe do Pedro (10 meses)</div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium italic text-brand-900/80 leading-relaxed">"Minha vida mudou depois dessas receitas! O Pedro não comia nada, chorava no cadeirão... agora ele devora o pratinho sozinho e eu fico em paz."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-50/30 p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-brand-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 items-center reveal">
                    <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/julia_mom/100/100" class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md" alt="Juliana" referrerPolicy="no-referrer" />
                    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
                        <div class="font-bold text-brand-900 text-lg">Juliana Mendes</div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-orange-600 font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Mãe da Alice (1 ano)</div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-medium italic text-brand-900/80 leading-relaxed">"Os bônus sobre comportamento alimentar são incríveis. Valeu cada centavo, super recomendo para quem está perdida na introdução alimentar!"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Oferta Principal - ATUALIZADA -->
        <div class="card border-4 border-brand-500 shadow-2xl relative overflow-visible reveal" id="comprar">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-brand-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest inline-block mb-8">Oferta de Lançamento</div>
                
                <div class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-left max-w-sm mx-auto p-5 bg-brand-50 rounded-2xl border border-brand-100">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-bold text-brand-900 text-sm">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        + de 101 Receitinhas Saudáveis
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-bold text-brand-900 text-sm">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        Bônus 1: Meu Filho Não Quer Comer? O que fazer?
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 font-bold text-brand-900 text-sm">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 shrink-0"></i>
                        Bônus 2: Lista de Alimentos Saudáveis e seus beneficios
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="text-xl italic">De <s class="text-red-500">R$49,90</s> por apenas</div>
                <div class="text-7xl text-brand-600 font-black font-display my-4 leading-none">R$14,90</div>
                
                <a href="#" class="btn-gradient w-full block text-lg text-white font-black py-5 px-8 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide mt-6 animate-pulse-cta text-center">
                    QUERO MEU COMBO AGORA
                </a>

                <div class="mt-10 bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-green-100 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
                    <div class="relative w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div class="absolute bg-brand-500 text-white w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-12 h-12"></i>
                        </div>
                        <img 
                            src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuanFaria/luvics/0ce6f63412b182f767a4edda7ec97e8df6a7e937/pratinho/imagens/selo.png" 
                            class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-md z-10 relative opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" 
                            alt="Garantia"
                            referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
                            onload="this.style.opacity='1'"
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-700 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-wide">
                        <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-5 h-5"></i> Pagamento 100% Seguro
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ -->
        <div class="card reveal" x-data="{ open: null }">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-black text-brand-800 mb-6 text-center">Dúvidas Frequentes</h2>
            <div class="border border-brand-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                <template x-for="(faq, i) in [
                    {q: 'Como recebo o acesso?', a: 'O acesso é imediato! Assim que o seu pagamento for confirmado, você receberá os produtos diretamente da plataforma da Kiwify.'},
                    {q: 'O material é digital?', a: 'Sim, o material está em formato PDF de altíssima qualidade, pronto para ser lido no celular, tablet ou computador. Você também pode imprimir se preferir ter o livrinho físico na cozinha!'},
                    {q: 'Para qual idade são as receitas?', a: 'As receitas são focadas na Introdução Alimentar (a partir dos 6 meses) até os 2 anos de idade, garantindo uma base nutricional sólida.'},
                    {q: 'Por quanto tempo terei acesso?', a: 'O acesso é VITALÍCIO. O material é seu para sempre, pode baixar quantas vezes quiser!'}
                ]" :key="i">
                    <div class="border-b border-brand-100 last:border-0">
                        <button @click="open = (open === i ? null : i)" class="w-full flex justify-between p-4 font-bold text-brand-900 text-left items-center text-sm">
                            <span x-text="faq.q"></span>
                            <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform" :class="open === i ? 'rotate-180' : ''"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div x-show="open === i" x-cloak x-transition class="px-4 pb-4 text-xs opacity-75 text-left" x-text="faq.a"></div>
                    </div>
                </template>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Garantia Risco Zero -->
        <div class="card text-center relative mt-16 overflow-visible reveal">
            <div class="absolute -top-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-20">
                <div class="relative w-24 h-24 animate-pulse-soft flex items-center justify-center">
                    <div class="absolute bg-brand-500 text-white w-20 h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                        <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-12 h-12"></i>
                    </div>
                    <img 
                        src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LuanFaria/luvics/0ce6f63412b182f767a4edda7ec97e8df6a7e937/pratinho/imagens/selo.png" 
                        class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-xl z-10 relative opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" 
                        alt="Garantia"
                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
                        onload="this.style.opacity='1'"
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-12">
                <h2 class="font-display font-black text-2xl text-brand-800 uppercase">Risco Zero</h2>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-brand-900/80 px-6 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                    Se você não amar o material em até 7 dias, devolvemos seu dinheiro sem burocracia.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="mt-12 text-center pb-24 text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-brand-900/30 tracking-[0.2em] reveal">
            Luvics Pratinho<br><br>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
                <a href="#" class="underline">Privacidade</a>
                <a href="#" class="underline">Termos</a>
            </div>
        </footer>

    </main>

    <!-- Floating Button pulsando -->
    <div x-show="showSticky" 
         x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300"
         x-transition:enter-start="translate-y-full opacity-0"
         x-transition:enter-end="translate-y-0 opacity-100"
         x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-300"
         x-transition:leave-start="translate-y-0 opacity-100"
         x-transition:leave-end="translate-y-full opacity-0"
         class="fixed bottom-6 left-0 right-0 px-4 z-[100]" x-cloak>
        <a href="#comprar" class="max-w-[400px] mx-auto btn-gradient animate-pulse-cta flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-white font-black py-4 px-8 rounded-full shadow-2xl text-center">
            <i data-lucide="shopping-cart" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
            COMPRAR COMBO AGORA
        </a>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
